{"tid":1614634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【圖輯】【929／10.1行動匯報】即使身處英國，手足依然喺另一崗位為香港奮鬥！","createTime":"2019-10-03T00:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:14:29.000Z","uid":108502,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6326122ab255e743b0e19f1948756d5ebc51de96","tid":1614634,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:24:46.000Z","msg":"首先要為英國公海谷宣傳下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經過一連串嘅行動，各大城市／地區都已經組織到一班手足，而未來亦會繼續舉辦唔同嘅集會／宣傳活動！！<br />\n所以請各位英國巴絲速速入谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/C5voK1egJWHZDjxFqNnzDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FC5voK1egJWHZDjxFqNnzDw&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7ICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=dc7e8d35\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/C5voK1egJWHZDjxFqNnzDw</a> <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> (註: 請於入谷後回答簡單數學題)</span></span><br />\n如果想加入唔同嘅地區谷協助籌備活動，亦可以喺公海谷留言，到時admin會加你入行動谷~<br />\n<br />\n然後就交代返兩日嘅行動：<br />\n首先喺929，為咗響應全球反極權行動<br />\n英國五大城市 Birmingham Edinburgh London Manchester Sheffield 分別有集會同街站！<br />\n每個地方都有唔少當地人支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手足亦努力向當地人解說 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且巴絲們亦都準備咗唔同嘅方法去同當地人互動，帶出我哋嘅訊息！<br />\n(為免太多一次過太多圖 部分相會貼link)<br />\n另外亦分享返<br />\n其實世界各地都有手足舉辦反極權行動！<br />\n可以睇返全球集氣facebook page <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/globalsolidarityHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FglobalsolidarityHK%2F&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7ICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=68df21c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/globalsolidarityHK/</a><br />\n<br />\nBirmingham:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DO0gEMq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDO0gEMq.jpg&h=cd2484a