 />"},{"pid":"19f6c18e1470fbbb811821c96a1be3e1604d96f6","tid":1614634,"uid":27647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:25:10.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"a888deb52f035d59ddf1e32888e94022cc8a3ec5","tid":1614634,"uid":108502,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T00:25:22.000Z","msg":"之後手足更加喺十一再接再厲，襯住國殤日賀佢老母！<br />\n倫敦嘅手足直程踩落中國大使館贈興<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NsoFneK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNsoFneK.jpg&h=11b408a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YXkgE1p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYXkgE1p.jpg&h=42cca641&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n之後就去返Piccadilly Circus集會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T41GQ9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT41GQ9p.jpg&h=a4320b8f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5kPZ2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5kPZ2L.jpg&h=7db06275&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGA8v9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGA8v9r.jpg&h=fe85feca&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n亦有大合唱榮光！<a href=\"https://streamable.com/mmjl5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fmmjl5&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7ICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=397d92b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/mmjl5</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而Manchester嘅手足喺大學擺街站就遇上小粉紅留學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後演變成隔住馬路嘅叫陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3dvDTpk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dvDTpk.jpg&h=2c78720c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sNdufCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNdufCE.jpg&h=7a6191e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/tzbzn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Ftzbzn&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7ICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=7027489f\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/tzbzn</a><br />\n<br />\n中國人: One China! 手足: Two Systems!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/q46su\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fq46su&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7ICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=013a627b\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/q46su</a><br />\n中國人: Love China! 手足: Use your brain!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/kadvi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fkadvi&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7ICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=3719aeb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/kadvi</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n喺Birmingham，巴絲們就再次舉辦集會傳達香港人嘅心聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jr5MhSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjr5MhSa.jpg&h=d504a44b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/eptbs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Feptbs&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7ICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=533c93c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/eptbs</a><br />\n<br />\nEdinburgh嘅手足就喺大學校園full gear行街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEOJ4x2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEOJ4x2.jpg&h=55a01777&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b1edHjK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb1edHjK.jpg&h=82c9a781&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tHoFnjF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=